headline: Al Gore’s Investment Firm Sells Amazon Stock, Exits Mastercard, and Buys Visa
summary: Generation Investment Management slashed two-thirds of its Amazon investment, sold all its Mastercard stock, and doubled down on Visa.

headline: Americans Pull Back From an Epic Credit-Card Binge
summary: Credit-card spending is growing more slowly than debit-card spending for the first stretch in years.
